GOOGLE MAPS
-check out google maps demo in AA repo
-figaro install: makes config/application a YAML file,
--drop any API keys into the figaro file and it will be hashed
--<% api_key = "ley=ENV[GOOLE_API]" %>
-declared with new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById('element'))
-place the element in the DOM, then initialize the map - otherwise it will not appear.
-the map container must fill 100% of its parent div
-map locations can be stored in the database with longitude and latitude floats
-when in doubt, check out the google maps documentation
-google.maps.addListener(this._map, 'click', function_to_do)
